description:
It worked out so nice we brought her back twice... in a row! Mallie Fox is back for a second week of supernatural News, joining Tim while Dave is away in England! They talk about Clown Motels for sale, why being attacked by a haunted doll may not be all that terrifying, and being attacked by itty bitty sea monsters!!

Mallie Fox: https://www.paranormalgirl.com/
